Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Modern Shogi\NFamous Matches Chosen by\NShogi Players
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really need to get curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The last piece of fried chicken...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today's game is in the sixth block\Nof the Lion King tournament.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My opponent is Harunobu Nikaidou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is my first game after becoming\Na professional player.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:42.87,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Harunobu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When summer vacation hits,\Nshogi tournaments for children{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}are held on the roof of a department store.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before joining the federation,\Nstrong kids from around the country{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}participate in a number\Nof small tournaments like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harunobu and I were regulars\Nat events like that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so we'd already met many times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Children's\NShogi Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What grade was I in at that time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was terribly hot at that event,\Nand I was facing Harunobu in the semifinals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It really was hellishly hot that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He couldn't handle the heat well,\Nand was so flushed he looked like a red ogre,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and looked like he was in pain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looking at him made me feel terrible as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the afternoon, the wind died down,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}while the temperature kept climbing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think he was anemic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His face was getting paler by the minute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe it was an arrogant thought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but I was looking\Nfor the shortest way to checkmate him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought I should get the boy\Nsitting in front of me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}into a cool, air-conditioned room\Nas soon as possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...in the final stage,\Nas his imminent defeat became clear{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he put every piece he had into his army,\Nand began a desperate act of resistance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A silent scream escaped\Nout of his sweaty, pale face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that moment,\NI was ashamed of my arrogance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The human sitting in front of me,\Ndrenched in sweat and reeling from the sun,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was here because he wanted to win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I don't want to lose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it was something that couldn't be helped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it was going to be a long battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The victory was already mine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he struggled on, one move at a time,\Nsearching for a path that couldn't be found.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, he finally ran out of moves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how closely he looked,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there was no path for his king to survive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After muttering that, he began to shed\Ngreat big tears, just like in a manga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amid the crying of the cicadas\Nand the department store's background music,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I silently gazed at him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would be the face I'd probably be\Nsitting across for decades to come.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Becoming a pro...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is like jumping onto a moving train\Nthat doesn't stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can never get off of it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not until you lose and fall off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this small universe,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's an endless cycle of winning and losing\Nuntil you start losing your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As you gasp, "I don't want to lose".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go take a peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your rival is waiting for you\Nwith incredible spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The calm mind is the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:49.84,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHUBBY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:49.84,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's giving off so much fighting spirit\Nthat it's like an entirely different manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:08:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, "Next chapter,\Nit's either checkmate or be checkmated!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I envy you, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:10.70,CenterSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excite\NExcite
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Look at that fighting spirit.\NThat's all for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He said he was your lifelong rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Calm down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First, breathe in slowly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shallow breaths will narrow my field of vision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:34.26,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHUBBY\N(Actually, GRIN)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're late, Kiriyama!\NI got tired of waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I came at the appointed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're the one who arrived early, Nikaidou.\NGeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I guess my enthusiasm got the better of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}KNIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}2 - e - Knight. There it is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}2 - d - Silver General.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}3 - e - Pawn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Same, Silver General.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}1 - e - Pawn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's gotten stronger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's slowly but steadily attacking me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No good. I won't get anywhere\Nby just being on the defense.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to change the flow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}PAWN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sweat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the same as that time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He looks pale.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something's wrong with Nikaidou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, is the air conditioning working?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Something seems to be\Nwrong with it lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's heaven compared to the roof\Nof that department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}LANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}5 - g - Lance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's coming in where I don't have pawns.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I'll do this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}7 - f - Pawn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Silver General
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}6 - h - Silver General?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Silver General
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Instead of taking gold, he moved silver?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to lose either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Calm down. Take deep breaths.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Expand your field of vision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I keep my composure,\Nthis board should be in my favor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Calm down and keep playing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The game continued until evening.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I continued to shake off\NHarunobu's tenacious attacks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a move. I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, that's right. This face...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the same face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It hasn't changed at all since we were kids.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nikaidou...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and me too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...will stay like this forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and ever and ever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Harunobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hanaoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SOUVENIR
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about your vacation?\NWhat happened to traveling around the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you weren't coming back\Nfor 80 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had your mother take my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Thank you, Hanaoka!\NAre you sure it's okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ten days were plenty for me,\Nand it was a very satisfying trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I'll be going, then!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, being separated from you\Nmade me worry a lot, Master Harunobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was in danger of having\Nan irregular heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}*Didn't refresh at all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't gone to the hospital yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see Dr. Morikawa right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've already called him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in pain, Master Harunobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your kidneys aren't functioning well again,\Nare they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry. While I was gone,\Nyou probably weren't eating well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Hanaoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Subsisting on hospital food alone\Nbuilds up stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's been this way since you were a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen how hard it's been for you\Nall of these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all right, I'm here for you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take our time and get your health back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And with Mr. Kiriyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...how did the match go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know how strong he'd gotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I won't lose next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Master Harunobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:10.99,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Harunobu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:14.99,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the Night Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After my game with Nikaidou,\NI went to their house as promised.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Come over again after your match is over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}That's the last day of Obon,\Nso I'll make plenty of food.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. It's Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's late. I bet you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Momo. Rei is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I brought pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I knew you'd be late,\Nso I plated them separately for you, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a9}Downtown Specialty\NVarious Foods Triathlon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I know you have a small appetite,\Nso I put them in small portions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It all looks delicious.\NBut I wonder if I can eat everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this is for Grandma and Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I plated them using Momo's doll set.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TINY...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}- What's that? What's that?\N- I want it, I want it, I want it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:27.65,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GLARE GLARE\NGLARE GLARE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess two beers is too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ooph...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't sleep yet, Grandpa.\NWe have to light the ceremonial fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Already after nine? You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's too late, Grandma and your mom\Nwill have a hard time getting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, you lit the fire in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That was to welcome them home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We light that around dusk as if to say,\N"Hurry home. We're all waiting for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when they go back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we light the fire after dinner, saying,\N"We want you to stay as long as possible."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And when they come home, we put out\Ncucumber horses so they can get here faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when they leave,\Nwe put out oxen made from eggplants
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so they can make a slow, safe return,\Nladen with the gifts we've given them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we see them off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They were all smiling as usual,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}but somehow a certain solemness\Npermeated the mood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seeing how they prepared horses and oxen...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Made a special feast...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worrying with everyone\Nabout welcoming and sending off{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the people who are no longer with us...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It just made me think of a sad ceremony\Nthat only brings back painful memories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we go inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo, let's take a bath and go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina? Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, manga. I forgot a new issue is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go with her, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's walking fast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where's she going?\NThe convenience store isn't that way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There she is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't call out to her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her voice caused a lump in my throat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure she was holding it in\Nwhen she was with the others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll go back in a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I listened to her sobbing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the doubts I had shut away\Nbegan to seep into my heart like ink.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stay here a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For me, when I think about\Nthe real family I lost...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gave up on crying about it\Nbecause I thought it was pointless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.87,0:22:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It made me sad to think about them,\Nso I tried not to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.58,0:22:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I chased them out of my head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I chased them out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chased them out...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...was that really the right thing to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}She's crying...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}...but I'm not.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}But the two of us are gazing up\Nat that beautiful,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}beautiful, beautiful July night sky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:00.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the Night Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:37.14,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.43,0:24:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you open it, it has to be like,\N"Wow! That's so cute!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.31,0:24:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina is troubled with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.56,0:24:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, little one.\NI shall ask you your name. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.69,0:24:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bodoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.48,0:24:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your wonderful friend is just like\Na nice, round, shiny ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.11,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, you picked up another stranger?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.15,0:24:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode of\NMarch Comes in Like a Lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.99,0:24:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Study shogi with me, everyone!
